reviewText: Really Funny Programs.  Sent this one to 90 year old friend.  Now she wants me to send more.  Are there any other Programs by this group?
Quirky, yes. But cannot help but laugh out loud. Characters you like and care about. Try it. I would very much like more, but, sadly, this is all there there is, at least for now.
I love these British comedies where they are more charming than in your face with over-worked humor! The writing is excellent and the actors are spot-on!
A back-door insight into British pop culture and humor. I doubt Winston Churchill would approve -- British pop culture has not improved over the past century -- but we laughed anyway.
